    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with the paintwork showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful use like small stone chips on the lower bumper. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, you will find a pristine cabin environment; it has been kept strictly smoke-free and pet-free. The leather seating surfaces are supple with very light bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the premium sound system to the heated seats\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It comes with a comprehensive service history, showing consistent oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine pulls strongly without hesitation, the transmission transitions through gears seamlessly, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. With deep tread remaining on all four tires and recent brake service, this car is ready for the road with no immediate investment required from the new owner.",
